Package: rho.graphics
Type: Package
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Title: Rho Async Graphics Artifacts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Renders R graphics asynchronously to declared devices and returns
    typed artifacts with dimensions, media types, hashes, and provenance. Worker
    rendering avoids dependence on the active interactive graphics device.
